---
import PostLayout from '@layouts/PostLayout.astro';
import CodeBlockInputCell from '@components/CodeBlockInputCell.astro';
import CodeBlockOutputCell from '@components/CodeBlockOutputCell.astro';

const { metadata_page } = await import('@portfolio/consts.json');
const { colors } = await import('@portfolio/consts.json');
const { svg_paths } = await import('@portfolio/consts.json');

const page_title = 'Ordenar listas em Python sem modificar a original';
const end_url = 'tips/sort-lists';
const description = 'Dica para ordenar listas em Python sem modificar a original';
const keywords = 'python, lista, sort, sorted';
const languaje = 'PT';
const image_path = 'https://images.maximofn.com/python_short_list.webp';
const opening_brace = '{';
const closing_brace = '}';
---

<PostLayout 
    title={page_title}
    languaje={languaje}
    description={description}
    keywords={keywords}
    author={metadata_page.author}
    theme_color={colors.background_color}
    end_url={end_url}
    image_path={image_path}
    image_width=686
    image_height=386
    image_extension=webp
    article_date=2024-09-08+T00:00:00Z
>

  <section class="post-body">


    <aside class="post-index">
    </aside>


    <div class="post-body-content">
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h1 id="Ordenar-listas">Ordenar listas<a class="anchor-link" href="#Ordenar-listas"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 2" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h1>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <blockquote>
      <p>Aviso: Este post foi traduzido para o português usando um modelo de tradução automática. Por favor, me avise se encontrar algum erro.</p>
      </blockquote>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Suponhamos que temos uma lista desordenada</p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">list</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">]</span>',
          '<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[1, 4, 7, 2, 5, 8, 3, 6, 9]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>E que queremos ordená-la, então usamos o método <code>sort()</code></p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">sort</span><span class="p">()</span>',
          '<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>O problema do método <code>sort()</code> é que ele modifica a lista original, se voltarmos a imprimir a lista vemos que ela está ordenada, e não temos a original.</p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Voltamos a criar a lista original</p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">list</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">]</span>',
          '<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[1, 4, 7, 2, 5, 8, 3, 6, 9]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Para ordenar uma lista sem modificá-la, podemos usar a função <code>sorted()</code></p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">sorted</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">))</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Se agora voltarmos a imprimir a lista original, veremos que não mudou.</p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[1, 4, 7, 2, 5, 8, 3, 6, 9]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>O mesmo ocorre se a quisermos ordenar em ordem inversa, podemos usar o método <code>.reverse()</code></p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">reverse</span><span class="p">()</span>',
          '<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[9, 6, 3, 8, 5, 2, 7, 4, 1]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Se imprimirmos a lista, vemos que está ordenada em ordem inversa e não como a tínhamos no início.</p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[9, 6, 3, 8, 5, 2, 7, 4, 1]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Voltamos a criar a lista original</p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">list</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">]</span>',
          '<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[1, 4, 7, 2, 5, 8, 3, 6, 9]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Se queremos ordenar uma lista sem modificá-la, usamos novamente a função <code>sorted()</code>, mas com o argumento <code>reverse=True</code></p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">sorted</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">reverse</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="kc">True</span><span class="p">))</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[9, 8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3, 2, 1]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Se agora imprimirmos a lista original, vemos que ela não mudou.</p>
      </section>
      
      <CodeBlockInputCell
        text={[
          '<span></span><span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">)</span>',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockInputCell>
      <CodeBlockOutputCell
        text={[
          '[1, 4, 7, 2, 5, 8, 3, 6, 9]',
        ]}
        languaje='python'
      ></CodeBlockOutputCell>
      






    </div>

  </section>

</PostLayout>
